OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780617775
OL,3,CThe secret mission to transport the
OL,4,CBayeux Tapestry to the UK from France
OL,6,FBy Lucy L. Middleton
OL,8,FThe Bayeux Tapestry will be displayed
OL,9,Fin London's British Museum this
OL,10,FSeptember - but first it must embark
OL,11,Fon a highly secretive journey across
OL,12,Fthe Channel.
OL,14,FThe 70-metre-long 11th-century
OL,15,Fartefact that depicts the 1066 Norman
OL,16,Finvasion of England is on loan to the
OL,17,FUK from France, and has reportedly
OL,18,Fbeen insured by the Treasury for
OL,19,Faround #800 million during its stay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
